-- Aeroflot signs deal to buy Boeing Dreamliners
-- 
-- Sat Jun 9, 2007 7:43am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/06/09/us-russia-summit-aeroflot-signing-idUSL0940802320070609

 

 ST. PETERSBURG, Russia  (Reuters) - Russian airline Aeroflot ( AFLT.MM ) signed a deal on Saturday to buy Boeing-787 ( BA.N ) Dreamliner aircraft at the St Peterburg International Economic Forum. 

 Russian business daily Kommersant reported on Thursday that Aeroflot would place the order for 22 jets at the forum, in return for Boeing cooperation in helping Russian planemaker Sukhoi develop a midrange jet.